urse Amount&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-colon\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px;\">:</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label\" style=\"width: 439.484px; height: 10px;\"><strong>$disburse_amount</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Further, I hereby undertake to repay the EMI\'s by way of NACH/Cash/Cheque on due dates.</p>', 2, 3, 2, 0, 0, '2023-02-23 03:22:02', '2023-03-15 01:09:40');
