(9, 1, 'Promissory Note', '<p>To,</p>\r\n<p>$company_name</p>\r\n<p>$company_address</p>\r\n<p>Dear Sir / Madam,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>We <strong>$applicant_name</strong> S/o: <strong>$father_name, $applicant_address </strong>and<strong> $co_applicant_name, $coapp_address </strong>and<strong> $guaranter_name, $guaranter_address</strong>&nbsp;have executed a Demand Promissory Note for INR <strong>$payable_amount</strong> /- (Rupees ) dated <strong>$disburse_date</strong> duly signed and delivered by me/us to you as security for the repayment by me/us to <strong>$company_name</strong> of any sum now due or which may hereafter be or become due by me/us to <strong>$company_name</strong> by way of loans or advances, notwithstanding the fact that the loans or advances or the account, may from time to time be reduced or extinguished or the balance in the said account brought to credit, the intention being that the said Demand Promissory Note shall be a continuing security for any borrowing by us at any time to <strong>$company_name</strong> .</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>', 2, 4, 2, 0, 0, '2023-02-23 03:23:09', '2023-03-15 01:10:13'),
(10, 1, 'Letter Of Undertaking', '<p>To<br />The Chief Loan Officer<br />$company_name<br />$company_address</p>\r\n<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n<p>Ref: POST DATED CHEQUES IN CONNECTION WITH REPAYMENT OF LOAN ACCOUNT $customer_code ( $type_loan)&nbsp; Rs.$loan_amount /-In consideration of your having agreed to grant continued to grant loan of Rs. $loan_amount /-(Rs.$loan_amount_rupees) in the name(s) of Mrs. $applicant_name / $father_name repayable in $emi_type installments of Rs. $EMI /- each along with the interest/ service charges as per contractual obligation. I/We hereby deliver to you the post dated cheques with particulars as under to be enchased by you towards outstanding liability in aforesaid loan account.</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 98.75%; height: 80px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.7637%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;S.No</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Cheque No&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 9.28273%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Date</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Amount&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.1477%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp; Bank Name&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp; Account No</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.7637%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 9.28273%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.1477%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.7637%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 9.28273%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.1477%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.7637%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 9.28273%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.1477%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.7637%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 9.28273%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.1477%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.7637%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 9.28273%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.5697%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 20.1477%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; height: 10px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>In case the above cheques are exhausted and other cheques are required in payment of the outstanding liability, I/We undertake to deliver the same to you.</p>\r\n<p>I/We hereby undertake to provide adequate balance in the account with the drawee Bank to ensure that the aforesaid cheques as well as other cheques which may be delivered by me/us in due course, as and when presented by you for payment, are honored and paid.</p>\r\n<p>I/We also undertake that in case any of the above cheque(s) is returned unpaid for any reason whatsoever, without prejudice to rights and privileges to recover the money in default, shall be entitled to initiate the proceedings against me/us under section 138 of Negotiable Instruments Act, 1881 and other relevant provisions of law for the time being in force at our cost and consequences.</p>\r\n<p>I/We distinctly understand that it is at the faith and belief of this undertaking that you have agreed to grant loan of Rs. $loan_amount/- in name(s) of&nbsp; $applicant_name / $father_name ($bank_name).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 2, 5, 2, 0, 0, '2023-02-23 03:23:44', '2023-03-15 01:10:44'),
