(17, 1, 'Agreement Letter', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>LOAN AGREEMENT</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">THIS LOAN AGREEMENT is made at&nbsp; <strong>$branch, Bihar</strong> on <strong>$application_date</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>BETWEEN</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>M/S $company_name</strong>, a company incorporated under the Companies Act,1956 and duly registered as <strong>NBFC</strong> with RBI bearing Registration No. 14.00970, having its registered office at: Plot No. 10, 10<sup>th</sup> Floor, Office No. 1001 and 1002, Cabin No. 1, Janakpuri District Centre, West Delhi, Delhi &ndash; 110058 (hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;<strong>Lender</strong>&rdquo; which expression shall unless it be repugnant to the subject or context thereof, include its successors and assigns) of the First part</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">AND</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mr $applicant_name</strong>, S/o/W/o/D/o <strong>$father_name</strong>, at <strong>$applicant_address Pan No. $applicant_pan Aadhar No. $applicant_adhar_no</strong>&nbsp;(hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;<strong>Borrower</strong>&rdquo; which expression shall unless it be repugnant to the subject or context thereof, include his /her heirs, executors,&nbsp; administrators and permitted assigns) and <strong>$co_applicant_name</strong>, at <strong>$coapp_address Pan No. $co_applicant_pan&nbsp; Aadhar No. $co_applicant_adhar_no </strong>(hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;<strong>Co-borrower</strong>&rdquo; which expression shall unless it be repugnant to the subject or context thereof, include his /her heirs, executors,&nbsp; administrators and permitted assigns) of the Second part;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">AND</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mr. $guaranter_name</strong>, S/o <strong>$guaranter_father</strong>, at <strong>$guaranter_address Pan No. $guaranter_pan Aadhar No. $guranter_adhar_no</strong>&nbsp;(hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;<strong>Guarantor</strong>&rdquo; which expression shall unless it be repugnant to the subject or context thereof, include his /her heirs, executors,&nbsp; administrators and permitted assigns) of the Other part.</p>\r\n<p>Lender, Borrower, Co - borrower and Guarantor shall hereinafter referred as &ldquo;<strong>Parties</strong>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p>Borrower and Co - borrower shall hereinafter referred as &ldquo;<strong>Borrowers</strong>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>WHEREAS</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>The Lender is a registered NBFC with Reserve Bank of India and is having a valid license from the Reserve Bank of India and is engage in the business of retail lending, Loan Against Stock, MSME lending, Secured loan, Personal loan etc.</li>\r\n<li>The Borrowers are individuals who have applied to the Lender for business loan of Rs. <strong>$loan_amount /- (Rupees $amount_in_word Only)</strong>/- for the purposes as mentioned in this Loan Agreement;</li>\r\n<li>The Lender, on the basis, inter alia, of the application has agreed to grant the loan to the Borrowers upon terms and conditions hereinafter set forth;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>NOW, THEREFORE THE, PARTIES HERETO AGREE AS UNDER:</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>That the Borrowers vide A Loan <strong>Application dated $application_date -</strong> bearing <strong>Loan</strong> <strong>Application No. $application_no had approached the Lender </strong>for a Business Loan of Rs. <strong>$loan_amount/-(Rupees $amount_in_word Only)</strong>/- on the terms, conditions and the purpose as stated in this Agreement.</li>\r\n<li>The Lender hereby grants to the Borrowers and the Borrowers agrees to avail from the Lender, a financial assistance of a Loan Amount on the terms and conditions contained in this Agreement. The Tenure, interest rate (&ldquo;Interest&rdquo;) and the schedule of repayment in respect of the Loan shall be as specified in Schedule 1 as set out herein or as may be amended in accordance with this agreement from time to time.</li>\r\n<li><strong>PURPOSE OF THE LOAN</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The loan being granted for Business Purpose only&nbsp; and shall be used by borrowers only for the expansion of business of borrowers at the all-risk of the borrowers. Loan is granted against collateral of stocks, Furniture, fixtures and household equipment. Further borrowers, Co-borrowers, Guarantors guarantee in personal capacity for the repayment of loan and due EMI as per the agreed schedule</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"4\">\r\n<li><strong> PERIOD OF LOAN</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Period of Loan under this loan agreement shall be&nbsp; as per disbursement letter.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"5\">\r\n<li><strong> FEES</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers agrees to pay to the Lender the fees as set out in Schedule 1. The borrowers hereby authorises the Lender to deduct these amounts together with applicable taxes from the Loan Amount. The borrowers hereby confirms that irrespective of deduction of such fees, the obligation of the borrowers to repay to the lender shall be of the entire Loan Amount along with Interest, and other charges together with applicable taxes in terms of this Agreement. The fees paid / deducted by the lender is to meet the out of pocket expenses and the same is non- refundable / non-adjustable.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"6\">\r\n<li><strong> DISBURSEMENT OF LOAN</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The loan amount after deduction of fees as mentioned above shall be disbursed to the borrowers and the mode of disbursement of Loan shall be online through Net-banking. The Loan Shall be Disbursed as set out in Schedule 1.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"7\">\r\n<li><strong> INTEREST</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The principal amount of the Loan outstanding from time to time shall carry interest at the rate of $interest_rate % p.a.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"8\">\r\n<li><strong> REPAYMENT</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Repayment in consideration of the Lender extending the &ldquo;Loan&rdquo;, the borrowers, co-borrowers and the guarantor shall jointly and severally repay the Loan along with Interest in accordance with the Repayment Schedule set out in Schedule 1 of this Agreement. The Borrowers hereby confirms having understood that the interest is applied on the principal and agreed to the method of computation of EMI and the effective or Annualized rate of interest as stipulated in Schedule 1. The Borrowers further agrees to pay the EMI as per schedule hereto and shall also pay additional interest arising out of the default in repayment of instalments, any other charges such as Bank charges, penal interest, Recovery visit charges, other pre-payment charge etc., as per schedule 1 together with taxes and levies as be applicable from time to time.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\" start=\"9\">\r\n<li><strong> PREPAYMENT OF THE LOAN</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers shall not prepay / foreclose any portion of the outstanding loan amount either in part or full during the Lock-in period (&ldquo;Lock-in Period&rdquo;) as set out in Schedule 1 of this agreement. The Borrowers may exercise the option of pre-payment post Lock-in-period, where applicable, subject to the Borrowers and the guarantor complying with the following conditions and at the absolute discretion of the Lender. After the expiry of Lock-in Period as provided in Schedule 1 hereunder, the Borrowers shall give the Lender a notice of 21 days intimating his desire to pre-pay the loan and the Lender may accept pre-payment together with pre-payment charges / foreclosure charges as specified in Schedule 3, hereto and such charges is payable by the Borrowers together with applicable taxes.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The amount pre-paid shall be first used to credit the overdue interest, recovery charges, bank charges, legal expenses if any, arrears of instalments, interest due up-to date for the current month, The current month EMI, foreclosure / pre-payment charges and other expenses and taxes due as mentioned in this agreement. If any amount remains after meeting the charges then it shall be adjusted towards the principal amount. If the entire amount due for prepayment is not remitted then the amount so received by the Lender would be treated as an advance payment of future EMI and will be adjusted to EMI month on month, as and when the EMI falls due for payment. The Borrowers hereby agrees that the Lender is not obliged to reverse the interest that may accrue on account of advance payment. The amount due under foreclosure should be paid in full by the Borrowers to the Lender to qualify the account foreclosure.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;10. SECURITY</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers and/or the Guarantor hereby agrees to create the following security (free from any charge) against the loan facility</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman; text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>All Stock/goods/Furniture/Fixtures/Assets owned/Kept at Address<strong><u> </u></strong>mentioned as office/home address of borrowers, guarantors and their legal heirs.</li>\r\n<li>Personal Guaranty of the Guarantor and borrowers.</li>\r\n<li>Movable and immovable Assets Owned by the borrowers, Co-Applicant and Guarantor.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;b. In consideration of the Lender granting the Loan and as a security for the same, the Guarantor hereby agrees to provide an irrevocable and unconditional guarantee against the loan facility availed by the borrowers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; c. The borrowers also agrees to provide post-dated cheques to the Lender equivalent to the amount comprising of the Principle amount along with the Interest and all other dues including but not limited to overdue charges, penal interest, recovery charges, Legal and visit expenses for the tenure of this loan agreement..</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;d. The Security provided under this Agreement shall be for repayment of the Loan together with the interest and other obligations herein of the borrowers and Guarantor towards the Lender.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;e. The liability of the borrowers and the Guarantor shall be joint and several. The borrowers and the Guarantor hereby agrees that the Lender shall have right of lien over all the assets of the borrowers and the Guarantor as mentioned above for the Loan availed by the borrowers from the Lender. The borrowers and Guarantor hereby agree that they shall not in any way, dispose of their assets without the prior written consent of the Lender</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; 11. EVENT OF DEFAULT</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The happening of the following events shall constitute an event of default (&ldquo;Event of Default&rdquo;)</p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Any non-compliance by the borrowers and/or the Guarantor of the terms &amp; conditions of this Agreement;</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Any breach of this Agreement by the borrowers and/or the Guarantor;</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Non adherence to the Repayment Schedule.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Insolvency, winding up, dissolution of the borrowers / the Guarantor and inability of the borrowers to repay their debts;</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Any concealment of any material document or event by the borrowers / Guarantor;</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Submission of any forged document by the borrowers/ Guarantor(s);</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Any other event which in the sole opinion of the Lender would endanger the repayment of the Loan Amount</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 12. CONSEQUENCES OF AN EVENT OF DEFAULT</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The entire Loan Amount along with Interest for the entire period shall immediately become due and payable, and the Lender shall have the right to recall the entire loan together with interest for the entire period, the additional interest arising on account of default, Bank charges and other Charges, as mentioned in Schedule 1 hereunder; All charges are payable by the borrowers together with applicable taxes.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lender shall be entitled to invoke the Security;</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lender shall be entitled to proceed against and take any action against the borrowers and / or the Guarantor(s) in order to recover the Loan Amount along with Interest, Charges and expenses;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 13. COST AND EXPENSES</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers and Guarantor shall bear all costs and other expenses incurred in relation to the completion of this Agreement and in complying with the terms and conditions of this Agreement, including any and all costs incurred in connection with this Agreement.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers and Guarantor hereby confirm their liability and shall reimburse / pay any tax that the Lender may have to pay to the Government, in respect of the transactions under this Agreement.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers and the Guarantor hereby authorises the Lender at the cost and risk of the borrowers to engage one or more person(s) / agencies to verify any fact or information furnished by, concerning and pertaining to the borrowers and Guarantor and collect of the outstanding amount and / or to enforce any security.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Any claim, demands, actions, costs, expenses and liabilities incurred or suffered by the Lender by reason of non-payment or insufficient payment of stamp duty by the borrowers under this Agreement and the documents and any other writings or documents which may be executed by the borrowers pursuant to or in relation to this Agreement, will be to the cost of the borrowers..</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 14. REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers and Guarantor represents and warrants that:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-roman; text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li>Their execution, delivery and performance of this Agreement are within their powers and do not contravene any contract binding on or affecting his / it or any of his / its properties, do not violate any applicable law or regulation;</li>\r\n<li>this Agreement is valid and binding upon the Borrowers;</li>\r\n<li>there is no pending or threatened action which may materially adversely affect the validity or enforceability of this Agreement;</li>\r\n<li>all information provided by the Borrowers to the Lender under this Agreement is correct and true.</li>\r\n<li>The Borrowers hereby confirms that the funds will be utilized for the purpose as stated in Schedule 1 and that the Loan will not be utilized for speculative purpose.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; b. The Borrowers and Guarantor will not seek to claim or recover from the Lender on any grounds whatsoever and/or in any circumstances whatsoever (whether now or hereafter existing), any purported damages or compensation, direct, indirect or consequential, for any acts or actions whatsoever of the Lender hereunder and/or in respect of the Loan and/or the Security, taken oromitted by the Lender in terms hereof and/or pursuant hereto and/or to protect any of its interests and rights as the lender or a creditor, and the&nbsp; Borrowers hereby expressly waives any right to seek or make any such claim or recovery on any grounds whatsoever.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;c. The Borrowers and Guarantor hereby accepts and confirms that he has no objection to the Lender administering the Loan through third Parties. The Borrowers confirm that the Lender may,either partly or in full delegate such of those activities to any third party as it may think fit in the circumstances. Such delegation of work, would include the right and authority to collect the outstanding on behalf of the Lender, the dues and unpaid installments and other amount due under the Agreement and to perform and execute all lawful acts, deeds and matters and things connected therewith and incidental thereto including sending notices to the&nbsp; Borrowers, receiving cash against issue of the receipt, cheques and drafts. For the purpose aforesaid as for any other purpose at the sole discretion of the Lender, the Lender shall be entitled to disclose to the third party the details of the Borrowers, the Loan, the outstanding amount and other information for effectively discharging the work assigned to the third Party and the&nbsp; Borrowers hereby consents to such disclosure by the Lender.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;15. INDEMNIFICATION</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers shall indemnify and hold the Lender and its directors, officers, employees, agents and advisers harmless against losses, claims, liabilities, or damages which are sustained as a result of any acts, errors, or omissions of the&nbsp; Borrowers, their / its respective employees, agents, or assignees, or for improper performance or non-performance relating to this Agreement or any other document executed thereof in pursuance to this Agreement.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 16. ASSIGNMENT</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is expressly agreed that the Borrowers shall not be entitled to assign, either directly or indirectly, the obligations set out herein.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender shall be entitled to assign its rights and obligations under this Agreement in part or in full to any third party.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender shall at time have a exclusive right to assign or transfer the loan account or any other incidental activity connected the loan account of the borrower to any other NBFC or any other third party without the consent of borrowers and Guarantor and without the obligation to inform the borrower.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender shall at any time, without reference to the Borrowers be entitled to securitize, sell, assign, discount or transfer all or any of the Lender&rsquo;s rights and obligations under this Agreement together with the underlying security to any person(s) of the choice of the Lender, in whole or in part and in such manner as the Lender may decide. Any such sale, assignment or transfer shall bind the Borrowers conclusively.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 17. TERM AND TERMINATION</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">This Agreement shall become effective on the date of execution.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Agreement shall stand terminated on the date the Borrower has repaid the Loan Amount in full along with Interest, overdue interest, Bank charges and other charges as mentioned in this Agreement, and fulfilled all other obligations under the Agreement to the satisfaction of the Lender.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrower does not have the right to terminate this Agreement in any situation except with the written consent of the Lender, by repaying the entire amounts due to the Lender under this Agreement.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;18. DISCLOSURE OF INFORMATION</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers accept, confirm and consent for the disclosure and sharing by the Lender of all or any information and data relating to the&nbsp; Borrowers, the facilities, any other transactions that the&nbsp; Borrowers has with the Lender, the Borrowers&rsquo; account, and the agreements and documents related to the facilities and transactions, including but not limited to information relating to default, if any, committed by the&nbsp; Borrowers, in the discharge of the Borrowers&rsquo; obligations in relation to the facilities or other transactions, as the Lender may deem appropriate and necessary to disclose and furnish, to the Reserve Bank of India (&ldquo;RBI&rdquo;) and/or to the Credit Information Companies and/or to any other agency or body as authorized in this behalf by RBI, to other banks and lenders including assignees and potential assignees, to its professional advisers and consultants and to its service providers instructed by it in relation to the Facilities, and/or as required under law or any applicable regulation, or at the order of a court of law, or at the request or order of any statutory, regulatory or supervisory authority with whom it customarily complies.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers undertakes and covenants that it shall provide all information, including information regarding other credit facilities enjoyed by the Borrowers, as and when required by the Lender. The Borrowers declares that the information furnished to the Lender from time to time is and shall be true and correct.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers hereby further agrees that in case the&nbsp; Borrowers fails to pay the Lender\'s dues or commits default in the repayment of the loan instalment(s) or interest thereon on due date(s), or the account of the&nbsp; Borrowers becomes Non-Performing Assets as per the Reserve Bank of India\'s norms, the Lender will be at liberty to disclose or publish in print and / or electronic media the photograph(s), name(s) and address(es) of the&nbsp; Borrowers as wellful defaulter along with the details of outstanding dues payable by such&nbsp; Borrowers, to the Lender.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers accepts that the RBI or the Credit Information Companies and or any other agency so authorized, or any statutory, regulatory or supervisory authority or other lenders / potential lenders, may use, process and disseminate the said information and data disclosed by the Lender in such manner as deemed fit by them in any particular circumstances and shall not hold the Lender responsible or liable in this regard.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers authorize the Lender to disclose, from time to time any information relating to the Loans to any Parent / subsidiary / affiliates / associate entity of the Lender, and to third parties engaged by the Lender, for the purpose of marketing of services and products and to its investors</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 19. GENERAL PROVISIONS</strong></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers is liable to repay the dues as per repayment schedule whether demanded or not.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers shall at all times adhere to the terms and conditions set out in this Agreement and any amendments hereto.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender shall have the right to appropriate the amounts paid by the&nbsp; Borrowers in such manner, at the sole discretion of the Lender.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers shall be liable to pay / bear all taxes including GST that may be applicable from time to time.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender shall at any time, at its absolute discretion have the right to combine or consolidate or divide into two or more of any of the accounts of the&nbsp; Borrowers accounts with the Lender and/or set-off or transfer or appropriate any sum or sums standing in the credit of any one or more of such accounts in or towards part or full satisfaction of the liabilities of the&nbsp; Borrowers on any other account or any respect.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">It is hereby accepted by the Parties that the amounts stated by the Lender as due from the Borrowers, shall be final and conclusive proof of the correctness of any sum claimed by the Lender to be due from the&nbsp; Borrowers in respect of this Agreement, a statement of account made out from the books of the Lender, without production of any voucher, documents or other papers whether in support thereof or otherwise and the Parties hereby agree that the same shall not be disputed by the&nbsp; Borrowers.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The right of the Lender to recover the dues from the Borrowers shall be exercised either by the Lender or its authorized representatives and the&nbsp; Borrowers hereby agrees to the same.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender shall be entitled to assign / securitize its receivables from the&nbsp; Borrowers and the&nbsp; Borrowers hereby consent to the Lender exercising such right.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The&nbsp; Borrowers shall not give or any other person who agrees to incur any obligation for the&nbsp; Borrowers in favor of the Lender, any monies or other consideration or remuneration, whether by way of commission, brokerage or fee or in any other form whatsoever or howsoever for giving or confirming the obligation.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The&nbsp; Borrowers shall during business hours permit the Lender to inspect the place of business / residence of the&nbsp; Borrowers and also agrees to produce any documents / additional documents as may be required by the Lender from time to time. Further, the&nbsp; Borrowers hereby agrees to permit the Lender and its authorized representatives to contact / meet the&nbsp; Borrowers at their place of residence for collection of dues under this Agreement.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The&nbsp; Borrowers agrees to pay all the applicable charges as per schedule together with all taxes as may be applicable from time to time.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Borrowers hereby agree that the&nbsp; Borrowers may seek any further loan facility from the Lender and any such further loan granted by the Lender to the&nbsp; Borrowers shall be repaid by the&nbsp; Borrowers on terms that may be communicated by the Lender to the&nbsp; Borrowers from time to time. For this purposes, the Parties hereby agree that any confirmation for further loan facility as confirmed and accepted by the &nbsp;Borrowers over the phone is binding on the&nbsp; Borrowers and that the&nbsp; Borrowers agrees to repay such loans granted based on oral confirmation (voice call), together with interest, month on month by way of equated monthly installments as may be communicated by the Lender</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Extra-ordinary Circumstances No extra- ordinary or other circumstances shall have occurred which shall make it improbable to the Borrowers to fulfill his obligations under this Agreement</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;20. JURISDICTION AND GOVERNING LAW</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Both the parties hereby agrees that the present agreement shall be governed and construed in accordance with the laws of India and the parties hereto submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Courts, situate at Delhi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; 21. WAIVER</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender&rsquo;s failure to exercise or delay in exercising any right, power, privilege or remedy under the Agreement will not operate as a waiver or acquiescence, nor will any single or partial exercise of any right, power, privilege or remedy prevent any further or exercise of any other right, power, privilege or remedy</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; 22. SEVERABILITY</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If any provision of this Agreement is invalid, unenforceable or prohibited by law, this Agreement shall be considered divisible as to such provision and such provision, shall be inoperative and shall not be part of the consideration moving from either Party hereto to the other, and the remainder of this Agreement shall be valid, binding and of like effect as though such provision was not included herein.</p>\r\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>NOTICE</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Notices Every notice, request, demand or other communication under this Agreement shall:</p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">be in writing, delivered by hand, or by registered post / Speed post, acknowledgement due, or by Courier or any other mode as decided by the Lender;</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">be deemed to have been received by the borrowers and / or Guarantor when delivered by hand, at the time so delivered if during business hours on a business day for the recipient, and if given by registered post acknowledgement due, 72 hours after it has been put into post; and</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">be sent to the Borrower to the address mentioned in Schedule 1 hereto and to the Lender at its office address first hereinabove mentioned or to such other address as either party may in writing hereafter notify to the other party.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Lender may (but not obliged to) send short message services (sms) and Whatsapp messages to the borrowers intimating him on the dues payable by him and may call the borrowers and / or the guarantor to pay any dues that is outstanding under the agreement.</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers hereby agrees to pay the postal and other charges as mentioned in Schedule 3 here to for each of the notices being sent to him / them.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The borrowers and the Guarantor have read the entire Agreement, constituting the above clauses including the Loan details and the terms of repayment, the fees and charges payable as clearly enumerated in the schedule to this Agreement. The borrowers and the Guarantor further confirm that the entire Agreement is filled in their presence and that the contents provided herein is explained in the language understood by the borrowers and the Guarantor.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Schedule 1</strong></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p><strong>SI No.</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p><strong>Particulars</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p><strong>Loan Ac Datail/Amount</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Customer ID</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$customer_code</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>2</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Application No</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$application_no</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Loan Ac No</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$loan_acc_no</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Loan Sanctioned Amount</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$loan_amount</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>5</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Processing Fees</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$processing_fees</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>6</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>GST 18%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$gst</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>7</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Amount to be paid ( Disburse Amount)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$disburse_amount</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>8</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Loan Period</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$tenure</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>9</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Interest ($interest_rate%) Flat per year</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$interest_amount</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>10</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Total Re-Payment</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$payable_amount</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>11</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>EMI $emi_type</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>$EMI</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>12</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>EMI Start Date</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>As per Disbursment Letter</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>13</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>EMI End Date</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>As per Disbursment Letter</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>14</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Overdue Charges</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>Rs. $over_due_charge + GST per day for the delay period</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>15</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Lock-in Period</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>6 (Months)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>16</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>For closer charge</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>5%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>17</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Cheque and ECS bounce Charge</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>5% of cheque amount or 750/- whichever is higher &nbsp;+ GST</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>18</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Legal charges</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>Legal expenses at actual or as ordered by the Arbitrator/Court/Authority</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>19</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Visit Charges</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>Rs. 1000+ GST for per visit in case delay in repayment of loan</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"6%\">\r\n<p>20</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"37%\">\r\n<p>Penal Interest</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"55%\">\r\n<p>6% per month on total Outstanding</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the Parties hereto, acting through their duly authorized representatives, have caused this Agreement to be signed in their respective names as of the date first above written.</p>\r\n<p>For <strong>$company_name&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; For Borrower</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(Authorized signatory )&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Name $applicant_name</p>\r\n<p>Name - Vinay Shankar&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Place</p>\r\n<p>Place &ndash;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<p>WITNESS - 1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<p>Co-Borrower Name $co_applicant_name</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table width=\"23%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<p>Name</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"9%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<p>Address</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"9%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<p>Contact No.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"9%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>WITNESS - 2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Guarantor&nbsp; &nbsp;Name $guaranter_name</p>\r\n<table width=\"28%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"15%\">\r\n<p>Name</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"13%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"15%\">\r\n<p>Address</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"13%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"15%\">\r\n<p>Contact No.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"13%\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 5, 2, 2, 0, 0, '2023-03-22 00:56:43', '2023-09-13 01:29:07'),
(18, 1, 'Disburse Letter', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>To</p>\r\nThe Chief Loan Officer<br />$company_name<br />$company_address</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Dear Sir,</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>This is with regard to the sanction of&nbsp; Loan Ac <strong>$loan_acc_no</strong>&nbsp;of Rs. <strong>$loan_amount</strong>/-(<strong>Rupee</strong> <strong>$amount_in_word Only</strong>) by your Company, I request you to disburse the loan proceeds by way of <strong>$company_name</strong> to my bank account details given here under:</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<table style=\"height: 120px; width: 659px;\" width=\"757\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 59px;\">\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-heading\" style=\"width: 167.172px; height: 10px;\">Name of the Account Holder</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-colon\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px;\">:</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label\" style=\"width: 439.484px; height: 10px;\"><strong>$applicant_name ( $customer_code)</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 31px;\">\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-heading\" style=\"width: 167.172px; height: 12px;\">Name of the Bank</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-colon\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 12px;\">:</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label\" style=\"width: 439.484px; height: 12px;\"><strong>$bank_name</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 59px;\">\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-heading\" style=\"width: 167.172px; height: 10px;\">Name &amp; Address of the Branch</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-colon\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px;\">:</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label\" style=\"width: 439.484px; height: 10px;\"><strong>$bank_address</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 31px;\">\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-heading\" style=\"width: 167.172px; height: 10px;\">Account Number</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label-colon\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px;\">:</td>\r\n<td class=\"pdf-label\" style=\"width: 439.484px; height: 10px;\"><strong>$acc_no</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 31px;