(3, 0, 'Home', 0, 1, '/', '', '<section class=\"faq padding-top padding-bottom of-hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"section-header section-header--max65\">\r\n<h2 class=\"mb-15 mt-minus-5\">Frequently Asked Questions&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"faq__wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"row g-5 align-items-center justify-content-between\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div id=\"faqAccordion1\" class=\"accordion accordion--style1\" data-aos=\"fade-right\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item \">\r\n<div id=\"faq1\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faqBody1\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">What is a Personal Loan?</span> </button></div>\r\n<div id=\"faqBody1\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" aria-labelledby=\"faq1\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion1\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__body\">\r\n<p class=\"mb-15\">A personal loan is an unsecured loan provided by Non-banking Financial Institutions and Banks. It is granted on the basis of criteria including employment history, credit history, income details, age, bank statement, and many more.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item \">\r\n<div id=\"faq2\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody2\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"faqBody2\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">How to Check If I am Eligible for a Personal Loan or Not?</span> </button></div>\r\n<div id=\"faqBody2\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"faq2\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion1\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__body\">\r\n<p class=\"mb-15\">To check your eligibility for a personal loan, you can go through our Credhub website and app. Furthermore, if you have any queries related to conditions concerning personal loans for salaried employees, you may reach out to our customer care executives..</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item \">\r\n<div id=\"faq3\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faqBody3\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">What are the Documents Required to Avail a Personal Loan?</span> </button></div>\r\n<div id=\"faqBody3\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"faq3\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion1\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__body\">\r\n<ul class=\"mb-15\">\r\n<li>KYC Documents- Aadhaar Card, Passport, Driving License</li>\r\n<li>Employee ID Card</li>\r\n<li>PAN Card</li>\r\n<li>Utility Bill</li>\r\n<li>Salary Slips of the Last 3 Months</li>\r\n<li>Other Documents</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item \">\r\n<div id=\"faq4\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faqBody4\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">Why is it Important to have a Good Credit Score?</span> </button></div>\r\n<div id=\"faqBody4\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"faq4\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion1\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__body\">\r\n<p class=\"mb-15\">Maintaining a healthy and good credit score, i.e., 750+, ensures low-interest rates on personal loans for salaried employees and quick approval. Your credit score reflects your creditworthiness and repayment potential. You must maintain it throughout the year; otherwise, your loan application may be rejected due to a low credit score.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item \">\r\n<div id=\"faq5\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faqBody5\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">Can I Apply for a Personal Loan Online?</span> </button></div>\r\n<div id=\"faqBody5\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"faq5\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion1\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__body\">\r\n<p class=\"mb-15\">Yes, you can apply for a personal loan online using the Credhub application or website. In case you face any issues, just let us know.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item border-0\">\r\n<div id=\"faq6\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody6\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faqBody6\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">What are the Offerings by Credhub?</span> </button></div>\r\n<div id=\"faqBody6\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"faq6\" data-bs-parent=\"#faqAccordion1\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__body\">\r\n<p class=\"mb-15\"><strong>The offerings by Credhub are mentioned below-&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Personal Loan</li>\r\n<li>Salary Advance Loan</li>\r\n<li>Travel Loan</li>\r\n<li>Medical Loan</li>\r\n<li>Wedding Loan</li>\r\n<li>Home Renovation Loan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion__item \">\r\n<div id=\"faq5\" class=\"accordion__header\"><button class=\"accordion__button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#faqBody5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faqBody5\"> <span class=\"accordion__button-content\">What If I Miss a Payment?